# Spatial Navigation First

Every interactive element MUST have tabIndex={0} and be navigable with keyboard and remote control.
Use focus management, react-focus-lock for modals, and restore focus on unmount.
The app targets Smart TVs with D-pad navigation via spatial-navigation-polyfill.
